# Large archives — please do NOT commit big .tar.gz/.zip files
# (this is what filled up our Gitea server on day 1).
# If you have model weights or data files you want to share,
# use a small sample (< 10 MB) or store them on the VM outside ~/project/.
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.zip
*.tar
*.7z
*.rar

